c: 9
v: 70
t: "Ngakube ayizange yini ifike kubona indaba yalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo yabantu bakaNowa no-A’d noThamud neyabantu baka-Ibrahim neyezakhamuzi zaseMadyan namadolobha abhubhileyo na? Zafika kubona izithunywa zabo nobufakazi obucacile, kwakungesiyena uMvelinqangi owona (imiphefumulo yabo) kepha imiphefumulo yabo eyazona yona"